Class OtherText

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tectonica.jonix.onix2.OtherText
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OnixComposite, OnixComposite.OnixDataComposite, Serializable

    public class OtherText
extends Object
implements OnixComposite.OnixDataComposite, Serializable

    Other text composite

    A repeatable group of data elements which together identify, and either include or provide pointers to, text related to a content item. Please see Group PR.15 for details.

    Reference name <OtherText>
    Short tag <othertext>
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
